HOME_DELIVERY.free_delivery_limit: 2000 Kč (pro členy Klubu Hanibal 1500 Kč) pro službu Balíkovna na adresu

SUMMARY:
DELIVERY OPTIONS: Home delivery via GLS and Balíkovna na adresu. Pickup options include Parcel Shops/Lockers (Zásilkovna, Balíkovna, GLS) and personal pickup at 3 physical stores.
PRICING: GLS home delivery costs 99 Kč. Free shipping is available for orders over 2000 Kč (1500 Kč for club members) on services including Balíkovna, Balíkovna na adresu, and GLS výdejní místa. In-store pickup is free. Standard pricing for pickup point delivery is not specified.
PROVIDERS: GLS, Česká pošta (via Balíkovna), Zásilkovna.
NOTABLE FEATURES: The store offers a relatively low free shipping threshold. Delivery to other EU countries is available. Key information about Cash on Delivery (COD), express delivery, and weekend delivery is not mentioned on the page.
WEBSITE ASSESSMENT: The shipping information is somewhat fragmented. The main delivery page details GLS, while other options and the free shipping policy are mentioned in separate sections. The absence of standard pricing for pickup points and information on COD makes the overview incomplete.
